<HEADLINE>
Exit poll: Opposition wins Mexican gubernatorial vote
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; Eds: LEADS with 7 grafs to UPDATE with opposition candidate in
Aguascalientes calling for peaceful transition, national media
declaring him the victor. Picks up 5th graf pvs. Gonzalez Gonzalez
in 6th graf is cq. &QL; 
 &UR; AP Photos AGU101-103; OAX101-103 &QL; 
