<SLUG> BC-Austria-Obit-Schwarzenegger </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Mother of Arnold Schwarzenegger dies at 76
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   GRAZ, Austria (AP) _ Aurelia Schwarzenegger, mother of action
star Arnold Schwarzenegger, died Sunday of a heart attack, the
Austrian Press Agency reported. She was 76.
	   Mrs. Schwarzenegger was visiting the grave of her husband in
nearby Weiz when she collapsed, the agency said. She was
transported by helicopter to the hospital in the provincial
hospital in Graz, where she died four days after her 76th birthday.
	   ``With the loss of my mother, my world has fallen apart,'' the
local newspaper, Kleine Zeitung, quoted Schwarzenegger as saying.
	   Mrs. Schwarzenegger had lived quietly in Weiz where her late
husband was a police chief. She was active in local wildlife
preservation programs.
	   reid
</TEXT>
