PRI102-104,109.
	   BUDAPEST, Hungary _ Hungary's Gypsy community marks the
anniversary of the Poraymos _ or Nazi Holocaust _ with an all-night
vigil ending at dawn Monday. HUNGARY-GYPSY-HOLOCAUST. Has moved.
	   WASHINGTON _ President Clinton is facing growing pressure to
reveal what kind of relationship he had with Monica Lewinsky, with
a key Republican senator saying sexual misconduct might be forgiven
and Democrats seeking a quick wrapup of the matter.
