	   The protesters also said they would stage a rally coinciding
with the arrival of U.S. ships on Tuesday, ITAR-Tass said.
	   Protesters have picketed outside the American consulate, and
regional governor Yevgeny Nazdratenko has called the maneuvers
inappropriate.
	   (nw/gm) 	   
