<HEADLINE>
Serbs press attacks in Kosovo after vowing that offensive is over
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; Eds: UPDATES with US envoy saying Serb offensive setback to peace,
warns of humanitarian catastrophe &QL; 
 &UR; AP Photo NY116 &QL; 
