rival soldiers clashed in a military barracks and the government
ordered the people off the streets. CONGO.
	   NEW DELHI, India _ Suspected Kashmiri separatists shot and
killed 23 sleeping construction workers on a remote mountain road
as part of their ongoing battle to free their predominately Muslim
territory from Indian rule, police said Monday. INDIA-MASSACRE.
	   AGUASCALIENTES, Mexico _ Mexico's leading opposition party
captured the governor's seat in the central state of Aguascalientes
Monday, a victory that gives it fresh momentum heading toward the
2000 presidential race. MEXICO-ELECTIONS.
	   PHNOM PENH, Cambodia _ Responding to opposition complaints,
Cambodia's election commission said Monday it had agreed to recount
votes from certain areas in last week's general election.
CAMBODIA-ELECTION.
