<HEADLINE>
Moscow promises closer ties with Santiago
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   MOSCOW (AP) _ The mayors of Moscow and Santiago, Chile, pledged
Monday to boost trade, production, and cultural ties, a news agency
reported.
	   Moscow Mayor Yuri Luzhkov and Santiago Mayor Jaime Ravinet
