<HEADLINE>
Butler says disarmament talks with Iraq on verge of collapse
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; URGENT &QL; 
 &UR; Eds: UPDATES with Butler saying talks on verge of collapse. &QL; 
 &UR; AP Photos Planned &QL; 
