 &QC;  &QC;  &QC;  &QC;  &QC;  APTV 1800 GMT OUTLOOK FOR MONDAY 3 AUGUST 1998  &QC;  &QC;  &QC;  &QC;  &QC;  &QC;  &QC;  &QC;  &QC;  &QC; 

