	   OUAGADOUGOU, Burkina Faso (AP) _ In an Aug. 2 story about talks
between Ethiopia and Eritrea, The Associated Press misidentified
the foreign ministers of both countries.
	   The story had them reversed. Seyoum Mesfin is Ethiopia's foreign
minister and Haile Woldetensae is Eritrea's foreign minister.
