<SLUG> BC-AP-Sports Digest,0533 </SLUG>


<TEXT>
	   WORLD SPORTS AT 0000 GMT
 &UR; CYCLING:
	   REIMS, France _ A day after the Tour de France ended in Paris,
members of the Dutch team TVM are questioned by police about banned
drugs found in their possession.
	   Slug-Sports-Cycling-Tour de France-Doping. Has moved.
	   By Emmanuel Georges-Picot
	   PARIS _ Flat tire or broken frame?
	   The scandal-plagued Tour de France is over. Now the sport of
cycling is coming to terms with the task of rebuilding its tattered
image.
	   Slug-Sports-Cycling in Turmoil. Has moved.
	   By Andreas Avagora
